name: RubyDAO
description: RubyOrigin.io is a member of Solana Ecosystem. Let's own the NFT marketplace by the community. RubyDAO is developing a web3.0 NFT marketplace, currently allowing users to create, explore and trade Solana, Ethereum, BNB and Polygon based NFTs without any listing fees. RubyDAO DAO token holders and its community have the governance rights to decide the transaction fees to be received, items to be listed, you name it.
payDisclosure: Be part of the team in RubyDAO community.
